dct_title_s: Chart of the North and Baltic Seas &c. : showing the lines of steam boat communications, soundings, &c.
dct_description_sm: Depths shown by soundings and bathymetric isolines. Imprint from cover. Includes ancillary maps of "Harbour of St. Petersburg," "Port of Revel," and "Harbour of Heligoland." Originally issued in covers 18 x 11 cm. with cover title: A new chart of the North & Baltic Seas.
